942
00:43:13,180 --> 00:43:14,760
 problem muškarca i žena,

943
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:17,960
 a to je naša nemogućnost

944
00:43:17,960 --> 00:43:19,120
 da saslušamo drugoga.

945
00:43:19,120 --> 00:43:21,260
 Ja nekad ovako

946
00:43:21,260 --> 00:43:23,200
 završam upravo

947
00:43:23,200 --> 00:43:24,380
