949
00:43:25,480 --> 00:43:27,300
 moja profesionalna deformacija,

950
00:43:27,300 --> 00:43:28,940
 verbalna i neverbalna komunikacija,

951
00:43:28,940 --> 00:43:30,360
 ali tako nekakav malo

952
00:43:30,360 --> 00:43:32,160
