956
00:43:34,880 --> 00:43:36,880
 svakakvih ličnosti.

957
00:43:36,880 --> 00:43:39,700
 Ona, baš sam skužila,

958
00:43:39,700 --> 00:43:40,640
 pogotovo mi žene,

959
00:43:40,640 --> 00:43:41,900
