961
00:43:42,540 --> 00:43:44,340
 Znači ono,

962
00:43:44,340 --> 00:43:45,960
 samo čekaš da ova druga

963
00:43:45,960 --> 00:43:47,000
 udahne dah

964
00:43:47,000 --> 00:43:49,260
 da bi se ti ubacio

965
00:43:49,260 --> 00:43:50,100
 s nečim svojim.

966
00:43:50,100 --> 00:43:52,100
 Ono, uzme pauzu

967
00:43:52,100 --> 00:43:52,840
 jednu sekundu,

968
00:43:52,840 --> 00:43:54,240
 a ti si već ubacila

969
00:43:54,240 --> 00:43:55,020
 svoju priču,

970
00:43:55,020 --> 00:43:55,860
 šta si htjela reći,

971
00:43:55,860 --> 00:43:56,780
 nisi ju ni slušala.

972
00:43:56,780 --> 00:43:57,700
 Sam je očekala

973
00:43:57,700 --> 00:43:58,460
 kada ćeš izreći.

974
00:43:58,460 --> 00:43:59,600
 Ono, to sam skužila

975
00:43:59,600 --> 00:44:00,360
 par puta priča

976
00:44:00,360 --> 00:44:01,060
 sa o porodima.

977
00:44:01,060 --> 00:44:02,320
 Ono, ova jedna,

978
00:44:02,320 --> 00:44:04,020
