980
00:44:05,560 --> 00:44:07,140
 ono, skoro iskrvarila,

981
00:44:07,140 --> 00:44:09,560
 bilo je pitanje života i smrti,

982
00:44:09,560 --> 00:44:10,600
 a ova sama jedva čeka

983
00:44:10,600 --> 00:44:11,820
 da kaže kako je ona,

984
00:44:11,820 --> 00:44:12,800
 ono, skoro se porodila

985
00:44:15,960 --> 00:44:16,560
