987
00:44:17,480 --> 00:44:18,520
 savršen porod.

988
00:44:18,520 --> 00:44:20,620
 Baš se lako otvaram.

989
00:44:20,620 --> 00:44:21,880
 Bogu hvala,

990
00:44:21,880 --> 00:44:23,080
