993
00:44:24,660 --> 00:44:25,640
 samo što nije umrla.

994
00:44:25,640 --> 00:44:27,800
 Ili, prijateljica,

995
00:44:27,800 --> 00:44:28,840
 ti se žali kako ima,

996
00:44:28,840 --> 00:44:30,320
 ono, pet mašina veša

997
00:44:30,320 --> 00:44:30,980
