1000
00:44:32,880 --> 00:44:35,120
 Ne može sve jednostavno

1001
00:44:35,120 --> 00:44:36,100
 više držati

1002
00:44:36,100 --> 00:44:37,020
 u svojim koncima,

1003
00:44:37,020 --> 00:44:38,460
 odnos s mužem

1004
00:44:38,460 --> 00:44:39,120
