1010
00:44:46,860 --> 00:44:48,220
 imaš potrebu njoj reći

1011
00:44:48,220 --> 00:44:49,580
 kako ti je baš sve dobro

1012
00:44:49,580 --> 00:44:50,540
 sad u životu.

1013
00:44:50,540 --> 00:44:53,100
 Dijete ti spava 12 sati,

1014
00:44:53,100 --> 00:44:54,840
 šta god mu daš da si,

1015
00:44:54,840 --> 00:44:55,940
 sam se zaigra,

1016
00:44:55,940 --> 00:44:57,760
 ne moraš ti ništa ni raditi,

1017
00:44:57,760 --> 00:44:59,540
 odnos s mužem nikad bolji,

1018
00:44:59,540 --> 00:45:01,240
 uspioš i moliti svaki dan,

1019
00:45:01,240 --> 00:45:02,300
 bar sat vremena.

1020
00:45:02,300 --> 00:45:05,960
 A znate šta to samo znači?

1021
00:45:05,960 --> 00:45:07,960
 Samo si jako sebična

1022
00:45:07,960 --> 00:45:09,100
 i frustrirana.

1023
00:45:09,100 --> 00:45:11,120
 Da si zadovoljna sa sobom,

1024
00:45:11,120 --> 00:45:13,300
 tvoje srce je bilo

1025
00:45:13,300 --> 00:45:14,420
 otvoreno za drugu.

1026
00:45:14,420 --> 00:45:16,960
 A ovako,

1027
00:45:16,960 --> 00:45:18,900
 joj biti to samo iskaz

1028
00:45:18,900 --> 00:45:20,700
 tvoje nezadovoljstva,

1029
00:45:20,700 --> 00:45:21,680
 tvoje frustriranosti,

1030
00:45:21,680 --> 00:45:22,960
 jer te zadovoljava

1031
00:45:22,960 --> 00:45:23,860
 grijeh.

1032
00:45:23,860 --> 00:45:24,920
 To je biti grijeh.

1033
00:45:24,920 --> 00:45:26,360
 Zadovoljava te

1034
00:45:26,360 --> 00:45:28,020
 drugo ispričati

1035
00:45:28,020 --> 00:45:29,480
 kako je tebi super u životu

1036
00:45:29,480 --> 00:45:31,280
 dok ona grca u svome blatu.

1037
00:45:31,280 --> 00:45:36,520
 Jer da nije,

1038
00:45:36,980 --> 00:45:37,820
 tvoje srce je bilo

1039
00:45:37,820 --> 00:45:39,240
 otvoreno za njene potrebe.

1040
00:45:39,240 --> 00:45:40,600
 Ne bi bila ti usmjerana

1041
00:45:40,600 --> 00:45:41,160
 ka sebi.

1042
00:45:41,160 --> 00:45:44,540
 Ok, Bogu hvala,

1043
00:45:44,540 --> 00:45:45,180
 dobro ti je,

1044
00:45:45,180 --> 00:45:46,220
 ali ne moraš joj to

1045
00:45:46,220 --> 00:45:47,100
