1046
00:45:47,100 --> 00:45:48,960
 U sebi zahvali,

1047
00:45:48,960 --> 00:45:50,060
 Bože, hvala ti što meni

1048
00:45:50,060 --> 00:45:50,900
 trenutno nije tako,

1049
00:45:50,900 --> 00:45:51,420
 ali ja ne znam

1050
00:45:51,420 --> 00:45:52,420
 kad će od mog života

1051
00:45:52,420 --> 00:45:54,040
 nastat ogromna razvalina,

1052
00:45:54,040 --> 00:45:54,800
 šta će se dogoditi

1053
00:45:54,800 --> 00:45:55,360
 u mom životu.

1054
00:45:55,360 --> 00:45:56,620
 Trenutno ti hvala na ome,

1055
00:45:56,620 --> 00:45:58,320
 a nju ću saslušat,

1056
00:45:58,320 --> 00:45:59,860
 ako mogu je dati savjet

1057
00:45:59,860 --> 00:46:00,420
 i to je to.

1058
00:46:00,420 --> 00:46:01,320
 Utješit ju.

1059
00:46:03,320 --> 00:46:04,640
 A ne govoriti kako je meni

1060
00:46:04,640 --> 00:46:06,120
 odlično trenutno u životu.

1061
00:46:10,320 --> 00:46:17,840
 Ja baš dosta sam vodila

1062
00:46:17,840 --> 00:46:19,000
