1075
00:46:35,960 --> 00:46:38,160
 E sad,

1076
00:46:38,160 --> 00:46:39,080
 spomenula sam,

1077
00:46:39,080 --> 00:46:41,580
 tu ne mogu ne spomenuti,

1078
00:46:41,580 --> 00:46:43,200
 odnos muškavce i žene.

1079
00:46:43,200 --> 00:46:44,200
 Žene,

1080
00:46:44,200 --> 00:46:46,300
 kad vam muž želi

1081
00:46:46,300 --> 00:46:47,300
 izliti svoje srce,

1082
00:46:47,300 --> 00:46:49,360
