1086
00:46:53,140 --> 00:46:55,160
 iskazati neko svoje stanje,

1087
00:46:55,160 --> 00:46:56,500
 nešto što prolazi,

1088
00:46:56,500 --> 00:46:58,700
 onda sigurno nije najmudri,

1089
00:46:58,700 --> 00:46:59,740
 najbolji trenutak

1090
00:46:59,740 --> 00:47:01,080
 nagazit ga taj žonom,

1091
00:47:01,080 --> 00:47:02,740
