1093
00:47:04,340 --> 00:47:05,860
 evo sad je baš pravi trenutak,

1094
00:47:05,900 --> 00:47:07,200
 kad smo već načeli tu temu,

1095
00:47:07,200 --> 00:47:08,180
 da završimo sve.

1096
00:47:08,180 --> 00:47:11,140
 Pustite neko,

1097
00:47:11,140 --> 00:47:12,840
