1098
00:47:12,840 --> 00:47:17,600
 Prekrasne su riječi svetog pisa,

1099
00:47:17,600 --> 00:47:19,400
 muže vljevo se srce uzda u nju.

1100
00:47:19,400 --> 00:47:21,000
 I zaista nek tako bude.

1101
00:47:21,000 --> 00:47:22,660
 Budite mudre,

1102
00:47:22,660 --> 00:47:25,040
 saslušajte što on ima vama za reč.

1103
00:47:28,540 --> 00:47:29,080
 Ok,

1104
00:47:29,080 --> 00:47:30,560
 kao što sam rekla,

1105
00:47:30,560 --> 00:47:32,680
 mi često zbog

1106
00:47:32,680 --> 00:47:36,000
