1107
00:47:36,000 --> 00:47:37,400
 i rezanja svojih kapaciteta,

1108
00:47:37,400 --> 00:47:38,680
 jako često dođemo

1109
00:47:38,680 --> 00:47:39,860
 do dva velika grijeha,

1110
00:47:39,860 --> 00:47:42,460
 a to su manipulacija

1111
00:47:42,460 --> 00:47:43,300
 i kontrola.

1112
00:47:43,300 --> 00:47:44,300
 E sad, muškarci,

1113
00:47:44,300 --> 00:47:45,800
 ako ste do sad sjedili na ušima,

1114
00:47:45,800 --> 00:47:47,860
 vrijeme je da počnete slušati.

1115
00:47:49,920 --> 00:47:51,280
 Treze prvo pogledlja

1116
00:47:51,280 --> 00:47:52,720
 izreka obilno navještava

1117
00:47:52,720 --> 00:47:53,240
 kad kaže

1118
00:47:53,240 --> 00:47:54,200
 žena je muškarcu

1119
00:47:54,200 --> 00:47:55,700
 dana kako bi napredovao

1120
00:47:55,700 --> 00:47:57,060
 i uživao blagostanje.

1121
00:47:57,060 --> 00:47:59,060
 Međutim,

1122
00:47:59,060 --> 00:48:00,280
 zbog naših slabosti

1123
00:48:00,280 --> 00:48:02,140
 zajiništvo ljubav

1124
00:48:02,140 --> 00:48:03,000
 zna du se jako

1125
00:48:03,000 --> 00:48:04,960
 prometnuti u kontroli

1126
00:48:04,960 --> 00:48:05,900
 i manipulaciju

1127
00:48:05,900 --> 00:48:07,240
 koje su iskazu

1128
00:48:07,240 --> 00:48:08,280
 konečnici našeg

1129
00:48:08,280 --> 00:48:09,560
 dubokog, dubokog

1130
00:48:09,560 --> 00:48:10,260
 nepoštivanja

1131
00:48:10,260 --> 00:48:11,300
 prema našemu mužu

1132
00:48:11,300 --> 00:48:12,740
 i to je grijeh.

1133
00:48:12,740 --> 00:48:14,880
 To bi vas isto potaknula žena.

1134
00:48:14,880 --> 00:48:15,260
 Znači,

1135
00:48:15,260 --> 00:48:17,820
 ako znate

1136
00:48:17,820 --> 00:48:19,860
 ili ako ne znate

1137
00:48:19,860 --> 00:48:21,080
 ako ste i sada posvijestili

1138
00:48:21,080 --> 00:48:23,260
 da ne poštivate svoje muževe

1139
00:48:23,260 --> 00:48:25,100
 morate to ispovjediti.

1140
00:48:25,100 --> 00:48:26,440
 Znači,

1141
00:48:26,440 --> 00:48:28,540
 grijeh je potrebno imenovati

1142
00:48:28,540 --> 00:48:29,980
 i ispovjediti to.

1143
00:48:29,980 --> 00:48:31,760
 Za to je potrebno pokajati se.

1144
00:48:31,760 --> 00:48:32,820
 Znači,

1145
00:48:32,820 --> 00:48:33,520
 kontrola,

1146
00:48:33,520 --> 00:48:34,480
 manipulacija,

1147
00:48:34,480 --> 00:48:35,640
 nepoštivanje muža

1148
00:48:35,640 --> 00:48:37,000
 je zaista nešto

1149
00:48:37,000 --> 00:48:39,100
 gdje mi

1150
00:48:39,100 --> 00:48:41,260
 jako možemo povrijediti

1151
00:48:41,260 --> 00:48:42,020
 naše muževe,

1152
00:48:42,020 --> 00:48:43,080
 njihove identitete

1153
00:48:43,080 --> 00:48:44,300
 i njihove autoritete.

1154
