1841
01:10:01,340 --> 01:10:03,140
 Hvala.

1842
01:10:03,140 --> 01:10:07,660
 Nije rekla

1843
01:10:07,660 --> 01:10:09,400
 Bože, ali ja vršim

1844
01:10:09,400 --> 01:10:10,120
 volju tvoju.

1845
01:10:10,120 --> 01:10:11,720
 Zašto nisam u hotelu

1846
01:10:11,720 --> 01:10:12,520
 s pet zvijezdica?

1847
01:10:12,520 --> 01:10:14,740
 Ja ti služim.

1848
01:10:14,740 --> 01:10:15,780
 Rekla sam ti da.

1849
01:10:15,780 --> 01:10:17,340
 Kakav je ovo tretpan

1850
01:10:17,340 --> 01:10:17,980
 prema meni?

1851
01:10:17,980 --> 01:10:20,180
 Nego ona svejedno kaže da.

1852
01:10:20,180 --> 01:10:23,380
 Onda opet sjedna na magarca

1853
01:10:23,380 --> 01:10:24,820
 i zajedno sa mužem

1854
01:10:24,820 --> 01:10:25,880
 kojeg jedva poznaje

1855
01:10:25,880 --> 01:10:27,880
 bježe od Heroda

1856
01:10:27,880 --> 01:10:28,960
 jer žele ubiti

1857
01:10:28,960 --> 01:10:29,780
 njenog sina

1858
01:10:29,780 --> 01:10:31,380
 za kojeg si ti Bože

1859
01:10:31,380 --> 01:10:32,520
 rekao da je sin Boži.

1860
01:10:32,520 --> 01:10:33,340
 Vlasna sam.

1861
01:10:33,340 --> 01:10:38,040
 Onda prolaze

1862
01:10:38,040 --> 01:10:39,060
