1863
01:10:39,060 --> 01:10:41,080
 Josip umire.

1864
01:10:41,080 --> 01:10:45,460
 Isus jednog dana

1865
01:10:45,460 --> 01:10:46,700
 izlazi iz svoje kuće.

1866
01:10:46,700 --> 01:10:50,000
 Odlazi kod svoga rođaka

1867
01:10:50,000 --> 01:10:50,760
 Ivana Krstitelja

1868
01:10:50,760 --> 01:10:51,320
 da ga krsti.

1869
01:10:51,320 --> 01:10:52,320
 I Marija zna.

1870
01:10:52,320 --> 01:10:53,860
 Njena majčinska intuicija

1871
01:10:53,860 --> 01:10:54,460
 tada zna

1872
01:10:54,460 --> 01:10:56,000
 da on se više nikad

1873
01:10:56,000 --> 01:10:57,280
 neće vratiti isti.

1874
01:10:57,280 --> 01:11:00,220
 Isus se ne osvrće

1875
01:11:00,220 --> 01:11:02,680
 i ona svejedno kaže

1876
01:11:02,680 --> 01:11:03,480
 da Bože

1877
01:11:03,480 --> 01:11:04,360
 neka mi bude

1878
01:11:04,360 --> 01:11:05,120
 po tvojoj volji.

1879
01:11:05,120 --> 01:11:07,460
 Vrijeme prolazi

1880
01:11:07,460 --> 01:11:11,040
 neki uzdižu Isusa

1881
01:11:11,040 --> 01:11:11,860
 to je njen sin

1882
01:11:11,860 --> 01:11:12,660
 ona je ponosna.

1883
01:11:12,660 --> 01:11:13,980
 Po jednom trenutku

1884
01:11:13,980 --> 01:11:15,180
 čuje kako ga žele ubit.

1885
01:11:15,180 --> 01:11:17,020
 Zamislite kako to boli

1886
01:11:17,020 --> 01:11:18,040
 srce jedne majke.

1887
01:11:18,040 --> 01:11:19,340
 Ali ona svejedno kaže

1888
01:11:19,340 --> 01:11:19,580
 da

1889
01:11:19,580 --> 01:11:20,560
 neka mi bude

1890
01:11:20,560 --> 01:11:21,300
 po tvojoj volji.

1891
01:11:23,400 --> 01:11:24,460
 i onda dođe trnutak

1892
01:11:24,460 --> 01:11:26,800
 bičuju ga

1893
01:11:26,800 --> 01:11:29,120
 okrune ga trnjem

1894
01:11:29,120 --> 01:11:33,500
 rade najgore stvari

1895
01:11:33,500 --> 01:11:35,260
 protiv ljusovog dostanstva

1896
01:11:35,260 --> 01:11:36,340
 koji se mogu napraviti

1897
01:11:36,340 --> 01:11:38,420
 a ona svejedno

1898
01:11:38,420 --> 01:11:39,320
 prihvaća tu boli

1899
01:11:39,320 --> 01:11:39,620
 kaže

1900
01:11:39,620 --> 01:11:40,740
 da Bože

1901
01:11:40,740 --> 01:11:41,860
 neka mi bude

1902
01:11:41,860 --> 01:11:42,660
 po tvojoj volji.

1903
01:11:44,800 --> 01:11:46,120
 gleda Krista na križu

1904
01:11:46,120 --> 01:11:46,820
 raspetoga

1905
01:11:46,820 --> 01:11:50,640
 dijete koje ona rodila

1906
01:11:50,640 --> 01:11:55,060
 sina Božjega

1907
01:11:55,060 --> 01:11:58,140
 dok čeka odobrenje

1908
01:11:58,140 --> 01:11:58,680
 od Pilata

1909
01:11:58,680 --> 01:11:59,280
 da ga skinu

1910
01:11:59,280 --> 01:12:00,360
 i da ju ga daju naručje

1911
01:12:00,360 --> 01:12:01,520
 ona svejedno kaže

1912
01:12:01,520 --> 01:12:01,740
 da

1913
01:12:01,740 --> 01:12:05,000
 uzima ga u naručje

1914
01:12:05,000 --> 01:12:07,120
 mrtvog

1915
01:12:07,120 --> 01:12:08,440
 izranjavanog

1916
01:12:08,440 --> 01:12:09,120
 i kaže da

1917
01:12:09,120 --> 01:12:10,820
 zašto je ona mogla

1918
01:12:10,820 --> 01:12:11,520
 toliko puta

1919
01:12:11,520 --> 01:12:12,820
 reći Bogu da

1920
01:12:12,820 --> 01:12:14,380
 bez obzira

1921
01:12:14,380 --> 01:12:15,660
 na sve životne prepreke

1922
01:12:15,660 --> 01:12:16,400
 na sve životne

1923
01:12:16,400 --> 01:12:17,160
 poteškoće

1924
01:12:17,160 --> 01:12:18,100
 a ne vjerujem da bi

1925
01:12:18,100 --> 01:12:19,000
 jedna majka htjela

1926
01:12:19,000 --> 01:12:20,280
 proći to što je ona prošla

1927
01:12:20,280 --> 01:12:22,860
 pa čak i nakon

1928
01:12:22,860 --> 01:12:24,200
 uskrsnuća

1929
01:12:24,200 --> 01:12:25,560
 ona na pedesetnicu

1930
01:12:25,560 --> 01:12:26,460
 ulazi u gornju sobu

1931
01:12:26,460 --> 01:12:27,580
 s onim istim ljudima

1932
01:12:27,580 --> 01:12:28,600
 koji su iznali

1933
01:12:28,600 --> 01:12:29,180
 njenog sina

1934
01:12:29,180 --> 01:12:31,180
 i svejedno kaže

1935
01:12:31,180 --> 01:12:31,500
 da

1936
01:12:31,500 --> 01:12:32,580
 tu sam

1937
01:12:32,580 --> 01:12:33,340
 neka mi bude

1938
